<p>
  <span class="nym">Bernier</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Old High German, Old Saxon</span> <i>bero</i> 'bear' + <span class="lang">Old English</span> <i>here</i>, <span class="lang">Old High German</span> <i>heri</i> 'host, army'.
</span>
  
</p>
  
  


